emuInput.TitMainTitle: Portrait of baby Wesley Ann Fox, seated on sofa with dress spread out behind her, in Fox home on Apple Street, Homewood, horizontal format
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 31, 1955, pg. A17, reads: "ADORABLE! - Wesley Ann Fox, six-month-old charmer, dimples for her parents, Mr. and Mrs. Gerald Fox, of Apple Street. Although she was a mite young to know what Christmas was all about, she got a kick out of the grown-ups excitement. - Harris Photo."
